glossary.name: Sage
glossary.text: Mysterious group responsible for the creation of Gensokyo, both separating it from the Outside World and establishing its current social order.
glossary.title: The Sages of Gensokyo

glossary.name: Gensokyo
glossary.text: Is the setting of Touhou Project. Its culture vaguely resembles that of feudal Japan, heavily embellished with folkloric elements.
glossary.title: Gensokyo (幻想郷, "Land of Illusions" or "Land of Fantasy")
